'''Anoat City''' was a [[City/Legends|city]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Anoat/Legends|Anoat]]. It was the planet's only settlement.<ref name="GG" />

==History==
By the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the city itself had long been vacated.<ref name="GG" /> Directly underneath the abandoned city was a massive abandoned sewage complex, consisting of rusting sludge-soaked [[Durasteel/Legends|durasteel]] girder tunnels and passageways that made up the subterranean sewer system. The difficult to navigate, vast sewers were inhabited by [[Dianoga/Legends|dianogas]]; [[Moff/Legends|Moff]] [[Rebus (Galactic Empire)|Rebus]] chose that hostile place for his hideout and laboratory. He engineered a series switches that controlled an elaborate system of drain gates to keep any intruders away.<ref name="DF" />

[[Kyle Katarn]] [[Mission to Anoat|ventured]] into the sewage complex underneath the city in order to locate Rebus, who was also a weapons designer and contributed to the [[Dark Trooper Project]].<ref name="DF" />

